William Bryant (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Bryant_(actor) 0 William Bryant (born William Robert Klein January 31, 1924 – June 26, 2001), was an American actor. He is one of the more recognizable television character actors of the 1960s and 1970s. William_Bryant ( born William_Robert_Klein_January_31_,_1924 – June_26_,_2001 ) , was an_American_actor . He is one of the_more_recognizable_television_character_actors of the_1960s_and_1970s .
